explicitInput.esqlQuery:
TS metrics-collectortelemetry.otel-* | STATS BY service.instance.id, service.name 
| EVAL identifier = CONCAT(service.instance.id, " (",service.name,")")
| KEEP identifier
explicitInput.title: instance

query.esql:
TS metrics-collectortelemetry*
| WHERE @timestamp >= ?_tstart AND @timestamp <= ?_tend
| STATS
    Uptime = MAX(LAST_OVER_TIME(otelcol_process_uptime)),
    accepted_spans = SUM(INCREASE(otelcol_receiver_accepted_spans)),
    refused_spans = SUM(INCREASE(otelcol_receiver_refused_spans)),
    sent_spans = SUM(INCREASE(otelcol_exporter_sent_spans)),
    send_failed_spans = SUM(INCREASE(otelcol_exporter_send_failed_spans)),
    accepted_metrics = SUM(INCREASE(otelcol_receiver_accepted_metric_points)),
    refused_metrics = SUM(INCREASE(otelcol_receiver_refused_metric_points)),
    sent_metrics = SUM(INCREASE(otelcol_exporter_sent_metric_points)),
    send_failed_metrics = SUM(INCREASE(otelcol_exporter_send_failed_metric_points)),
    accepted_logs = SUM(INCREASE(otelcol_receiver_accepted_log_records)),
    refused_logs = SUM(INCREASE(otelcol_receiver_refused_log_records)),
    sent_logs = SUM(INCREASE(otelcol_exporter_sent_log_records)),
    send_failed_logs = SUM(INCREASE(otelcol_exporter_send_failed_log_records)),
    `CPU Usage` = AVG(RATE(otelcol_process_cpu_seconds)),
    `Memory Usage (RSS)` = SUM(LAST_OVER_TIME(metrics.otelcol_process_memory_rss))
  BY service.instance.id, service.name
| EVAL `Collector Instance` = CONCAT(service.instance.id, " (", service.name, ")")
| EVAL refused_all = refused_logs + refused_metrics + refused_spans, accepted_all = accepted_spans + accepted_metrics + accepted_logs
| Eval sent_all = sent_logs + sent_metrics + sent_spans, send_failed_all = send_failed_logs + send_failed_metrics + send_failed_spans
| EVAL `Receiver Failure Rate` = refused_all::double / (refused_all + accepted_all)::double
| EVAL `Exporter Failure Rate` = send_failed_all::double / (send_failed_all + sent_all)::double
| EVAL span_rate =   refused_spans / (refused_spans + sent_spans)
| KEEP   `Collector Instance`, Uptime, `CPU Usage`, `Memory Usage (RSS)`,`Exporter Failure Rate`, `Receiver Failure Rate` 
| SORT `Exporter Failure Rate`, `Receiver Failure Rate` DESC
